## ğŸ“„ Project Description

This project demonstrates how to dynamically generate a User Profile Page using **vanilla JavaScript**. It leverages core JavaScript concepts such as **DOM manipulation**, **element creation**, and **data rendering** from an object. The profile page is created entirely through JavaScript with minimal initial HTML.

